    "Warren W. Wiersbe": "; 18:13; 33:4\u20138). The image of blood on the hands (or the head) goes back to Genesis 9:5 [c_Gen_9] [v_Gen_9_5]  and appears in the law of Moses (Lev. 20; see also Josh. 2:19 [c_Jos_2] [v_Jos_2_19] ; 2 Sam. 1:16 [c_2Sa_1] [v_2Sa_1_16] ; 3:29; Isa. 1:15 [c_Isa_1] [v_Isa_1_15] ; 59:"
